     <div class="bookname"> 
      <h1>第666章、挑拨离间</h1> 
      <div class="bottem1"> 
       <a href="/10_10027/6708996.html">上一章</a> ← 
       <a href="/10_10027/">章节列表</a> → 
       <a href="/10_10027/6708998.html">下一章</a> 
       <a rel="nofollow" href="javascript:;" onclick="addBookMark(6708997,10027);">加入书签</a> 
      </div> 
      <div class="lm">
       推荐阅读：
       <a href="/10_10028/">神鬼剑士</a>
       <a href="/10_10029/">唐门高手闯都市</a>
       <a href="/10_10030/">位面娱乐大亨</a>
       <a href="/10_10031/">神武</a>
       <a href="/10_10032/">权倾一世</a>
       <a href="/10_10026/">科幻电影系统</a>
       <a href="/10_10025/">重生小地主</a>
       <a href="/10_10023/">步步封疆</a>
